name: XYZ
description: The XYZ class represents a point or vector in 3D space.

properties.name: IsZeroLength()
properties.description: Gets whether the vector is of zero length.

properties.name: IsUnitLength()
properties.description: Gets whether the vector is of unit length.

methods.name: Subtract(XYZ)
methods.description: Subtracts a vector from this vector.

methods.name: CrossProduct(XYZ)
methods.description: Computes the cross product with another vector.

methods.name: DotProduct(XYZ)
methods.description: Computes the dot product with another vector.

methods.name: Normalize()
methods.description: Normalizes the vector to unit length.

methods.name: DistanceTo(XYZ)
methods.description: Computes the distance to another point.
